      "span_text": "A principal component analysis was conducted to confirm the unidimensionality of the QuickDASH-JSSH-DS. The first factor had an eigenvalue (amount of variation in the total sample accounted for by that factor)  of 5.12, which explained the 47% total variance of the QuickDASH-JSSH-DS scores of the patients (Fig. 1) .",
